00:13:27.389 --> 00:13:31.140
Another girl, Nakagawa, enters and takes the
dish from Sakaki.

00:13:31.140 --> 00:13:35.760
Sakaki backs away as Nakagawa eats the poisoned
meal.

00:13:35.760 --> 00:13:39.600
Utsumi tells the girls that Kawada may have
a way to escape the island.

00:13:39.600 --> 00:13:43.329
The news brings them hope until Nakagawa starts
vomiting blood.

00:13:43.329 --> 00:13:47.649
Panicked, Noda takes a gun, demanding who
poisoned their meal.

00:13:47.649 --> 00:13:51.149
The girls point fingers at each other, which
causes Noda to open fire.

00:13:51.149 --> 00:13:55.439
With their trust broken, the girls shoot at
each other until Sakaki is the only one left.

00:13:55.439 --> 00:13:57.450
Hearing Shuya, Sakaki opens the door for him.

00:13:57.450 --> 00:14:00.129
She apologizes to him before running away.

00:14:00.129 --> 00:14:03.680
Shuya sees his fallen classmates, distraught
and confused at the chaos.

00:14:03.680 --> 00:14:06.579
He heads up the lighthouse and finds that
