instead.

00:14:16.089 --> 00:14:19.399
In the control room, Kitano is woken up by
his daughter's call.

00:14:19.399 --> 00:14:23.149
His family doesn't know his involvement with
the B.R. act but doesn't care where he is.

00:14:23.149 --> 00:14:25.619
His daughter insults him before dropping the
call.

00:14:25.619 --> 00:14:28.759
In the woods, Shuya struggles to move with
his injuries.

00:14:28.759 --> 00:14:33.649
He remembers his father and Nobu, which gives
him the drive to move forward.

00:14:33.649 --> 00:14:37.319
When it rains, Noriko heads out, hoping to
find Shuya.

00:14:37.319 --> 00:14:41.470
Instead, she finds Mitsuko, who aims a gun
at her, mocking her for being protected by

00:14:41.470 --> 00:14:42.470
two men.

00:14:42.470 --> 00:14:45.329
But Mitsuko runs away, seeing Kitano in the
woods.

00:14:45.329 --> 00:14:48.920
Shuya finally arrives, collapsing in front
of Noriko, who goes to help him.

00:14:48.920 --> 00:14:51.999
Kitano offers his umbrella to Noriko and leaves.

00:14:51.999 --> 00:14:57.629
At a warehouse, Sugimura finally tracks down
Kotohiki, but she hides from him, not knowing

00:14:57.629 --> 00:14:58.629
his intentions.

00:14:58.629 --> 00:15:02.490
In panic, Kotohiki shoots him when he runs
