00:15:05.980 --> 00:15:10.540
Confused, Kotohiki goes closer to him, demanding
why he still cares after she shot him.

00:15:10.540 --> 00:15:13.089
With his last breath, he confesses his love
for her.

00:15:13.089 --> 00:15:15.810
Kotohiki mourns, not having known his affections
for her.

00:15:15.810 --> 00:15:19.750
Suddenly, Mitsuko arrives and shoots her,
killing her instantly.

00:15:19.750 --> 00:15:22.680
Before she could walk away, Kiriyama fires
at Mitsuko.

00:15:22.680 --> 00:15:24.879
Thinking sheâ€™s dead, he takes her gun and
walks away.

00:15:24.879 --> 00:15:28.619
Mistukoâ€™s eyes open, using her stun gun
