00:15:28.619 --> 00:15:32.170
She swings her sickle at him, but his bulletproof
vest protects him from the slices.

00:15:32.170 --> 00:15:34.470
He kicks her off before gunning her down.

00:15:34.470 --> 00:15:37.930
At sunset, Shuya hears that Sugimura is gone.

00:15:37.930 --> 00:15:41.860
He decides to follow Sugimura's message and
go to Mimura.

00:15:41.860 --> 00:15:45.959
At the building, Mimura hacks the school's
security system while Seto and Iijima prepare

00:15:45.959 --> 00:15:47.509
the bombs.

00:15:47.509 --> 00:15:51.790
Mimura disconnects the officials from the
collars and disables the danger zones.

00:15:51.790 --> 00:15:54.399
The soldiers panic as the virus hacks their
system.

00:15:54.399 --> 00:15:57.910
Kitano walks to the fuse box and shuts the
power down, ordering the men to restart the

00:15:57.910 --> 00:15:58.910
system.

00:15:58.910 --> 00:16:02.929
Mimura and his friends load up the explosives
in a truck to take to the school, but Iijima

00:16:02.929 --> 00:16:04.889
spots someone in the woods.

00:16:04.889 --> 00:16:09.129
Thinking it's Shuya, Seto calls out, but Kiriyama
fires at him.

00:16:09.129 --> 00:16:11.580
Mimura fights back but runs out of bullets.

00:16:11.580 --> 00:16:15.360
He and Iijima try to flee, but Iijima is gunned
down, angering Mimura.

00:16:15.360 --> 00:16:18.190
With his friends gone, Mimura has nothing
left to lose.

00:16:18.190 --> 00:16:22.119
He climbs up the truck and triggers the explosive
just as Shuya and the rest arrive.

00:16:22.119 --> 00:16:26.139
The trio stares at the catastrophe in disbelief,
hoping for their friends to come out alive.

00:16:26.139 --> 00:16:29.959
Instead, Kiriyama walks away from the burning
