00:16:48.679 --> 00:16:51.499
He reveals that he's been pretending to be
on their side.

00:16:51.499 --> 00:16:55.720
Kitano hears Kawada fire his gun, announcing
that the battle is over.

00:16:55.720 --> 00:17:00.110
That afternoon, the soldiers retreat, leaving
Kitano alone in the school.

